<item>
            <title>[HIVE-15951] Make sure base persist directory is unique and deleted</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-15951</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In some cases the base persist directory will contain old data or shared between reducer in the same physical VM.&lt;br/&gt;
That will lead to the failure of the job till that the directory is cleaned.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
